data.description: This beautiful home is located in The River Plantation and is perfect for you! Three bedrooms, two full baths, dining room, safe room, oversized garage perfect for your cars & atv's. The kitchen is a chef's dream featuring a gas range, island and beautiful cabinets with all the extras. You will enjoy the open feel this home offers as the large living room opens to a huge outdoor patio area that features a fireplace and outdoor kitchen. WELCOME HOME!!
